Problem Statement : write a query to obtain the number  of users who purchased the same product on two or more different days.output the number of unique users


Tables : 

CREATE TABLE purchases (
    user_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    purchase_date DATETIME
);

INSERT INTO purchases (user_id, product_id, quantity, purchase_date) VALUES
(536, 3223, 6,  '2022-01-11 12:33:44'),
(827, 3585, 35, '2022-02-20 14:05:26'),
(536, 3223, 5,  '2022-03-02 09:33:28'),
(536, 1435, 10, '2022-03-02 08:40:00'),
(827, 2452, 45, '2022-04-09 00:00:00');


Solution : 
select distinct user_id from purchases group by user_id,product_id having count(distinct date(purchase_date))>1;

